OL,3,C'I don't need to win': Serena Williams
OL,4,Con her big comeback at Queen's Club
OL,6,FSerena Williams said she 'doesn't need
OL,7,Fto win' as the twenty-three-time grand
OL,8,Fslam champion prepares for her
OL,9,Fcomeback at Queen's Club in London.
OL,11,FThe 44-year-old has been given a wild
OL,12,Fcard for the women's doubles to play
OL,13,Falongside 19-year-old Canadian
OL,14,FVictoria Mboko at the HSBC
OL,15,FChampionships.
OL,17,FWilliams said she had "won more than
OL,18,Fmost people have in their whole lives"
OL,19,Fand she didn't have anything to prove.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
