PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781014279
OL,3,C'I don't need to win': Serena Williams
OL,4,Con her big comeback at Queen's Club
OL,6,F"I don't have anything to lose, and
OL,7,Feverything here is just a gain," she
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"I'm putting no pressure on myself.
OL,11,FI've had enough pressure.
OL,13,F"It's really about my kids getting to
OL,14,Fsee me play.
OL,16,F"It's also, an athlete is the best
OL,17,Fthing that you can be in the highest
OL,18,Fplace and having an opportunity to
OL,19,Fstill be able to possibly do that one
OL,20,Flast time is kind of cool and exciting.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
