FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781014279
OL,3,C'I don't need to win': Serena Williams
OL,4,Con her big comeback at Queen's Club
OL,6,FShe didn't rule out playing singles
OL,7,Fagain at some point in the future with
OL,8,F"a bit more training, but she was
OL,9,Fputting no pressure on herself.
OL,11,FBritish number one Emma Raducanu said
OL,12,Fshe was determined to get back into
OL,13,Fthe swing of things on home turf at
OL,14,FQueen's after crashing out in the
OL,15,Fopening round of the French Open.
OL,17,FRaducanu, who has battled a post-viral
OL,18,Fillness, played only one match in two
OL,19,Fand a half months before arriving in
OL,20,FParis, where she was defeated by
OL,21,FArgentinian Solana Sierra.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
