OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781014279
OL,3,C'I don't need to win': Serena Williams
OL,4,Con her big comeback at Queen's Club
OL,6,FAsked if she might follow in Serena's
OL,7,Ffootsteps and keep playing into her
OL,8,Fforties, she said: "Personally I
OL,9,Fdon't... I think it's an amazing
OL,10,Fthing. And I also think with sports
OL,11,Fscience these days and how everyone
OL,12,Ftakes care of their body, it's much
OL,13,Fmore achievable.
OL,15,F"But I have a lot of respect for
OL,16,Fanyone who comes back and keeps
OL,17,Fplaying for the duration."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
