OL,3,C'I don't need to win': Serena Williams
OL,4,Con her big comeback at Queen's Club
OL,6,FRaducanu reached the quarter-finals of
OL,7,Flast year's edition. This time, she is
OL,8,Fhere with Andrew Richardson, the coach
OL,9,Fwho guided her to the US Open title in
OL,10,F2021 and who she rehired last month.
OL,12,FThe 23-year-old is hoping to
OL,13,Frediscover some of the aggressive form
OL,14,Fshe felt led to that historic triumph,
OL,15,Fwhich made her the first qualifier to
OL,16,Fwin a singles major title in the Open
OL,17,Fera.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
