OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781014279
OL,3,C'I don't need to win': Serena Williams
OL,4,Con her big comeback at Queen's Club
OL,6,FShe remains the lone qualifying winner
OL,7,Fafter Poland's Maja Chwalinska ` the
OL,8,Fsecond qualifier to reach a Grand Slam
OL,9,Fsingles final in the Open era ` came
OL,10,Frunner-up to Mirra Andreeva at Roland
OL,11,FGarros
OL,13,F"I think a lot starts from the
OL,14,Fbeginning of the point of serving and
OL,15,Freturning," said Raducanu.
OL,17,F"I think that's highlighted on the
OL,18,Fgrass court, so working on the actual
OL,19,Fquality of the shot would be where I
OL,20,Fwould start.
