OL,3,C'I don't need to win': Serena Williams
OL,4,Con her big comeback at Queen's Club
OL,6,F"That's what I'm trying to focus on,
OL,7,Fand then it's easier to implement that
OL,8,Fmindset if you start the point in a
OL,9,Fbetter way."
OL,11,FBoulter will open her grass-court
OL,12,Fseason against eighth seed Leylah
OL,13,FFernandez.
OL,15,FThe 29-year-old did not flat-out
OL,16,Fdismiss the idea of pairing with
OL,17,FRaducanu elsewhere, but strongly
OL,18,Fsuggested Wimbledon was unlikely to be
OL,19,Fthe venue.
